            span <strong>L</strong>
            span ight of the world
          div 
            span 進入人群
            span <strong>I</strong>
            span ncarnational living
          div 
            span 網絡建立
            span <strong>N</strong>
            span eighbors and networks
          div 
            span 歷煉成長
            span <strong>E</strong>
            span xperience to grow


    section#services
      div.sectionsCover.color2
      div.container
        div(id='eventContainer' style='display: none')
          h3#header Come and join us in any of the events
          div#events
          div#findOutEvenMore.findOutMore Find out even more
      


    section#contact
      div.sectionsCover.color3
      div#gMap


